<i>♪ It's time for me to fly ♪</i>

56:18.958 --> 56:20.710
<i>♪ Time for me to fly ♪</i>

56:21.336 --> 56:24.255
<i>♪ It's time for me to fly ♪</i>

56:24.422 --> 56:26.841
<i>♪ Time for me to fly ♪</i>

56:26.925 --> 56:29.552
<i>♪ It's time for me to fly ♪</i>

56:29.636 --> 56:33.681
<i>♪ It's time for me to fly ♪</i>

56:35.767 --> 56:39.187
<i>♪ Whoa, baby, yes, it is ♪</i>

56:39.771 --> 56:41.022
<i>Whoo!</i>

56:45.693 --> 56:47.695
[crowd cheering]

57:02.502 --> 57:04.504
[song ends]

57:06.464 --> 57:09.259
[theme music playing]
